SYSTEM: Wiki: https://delicias.dia.fi.upm.es/wiki/index.php/FAOntology 

Dear all,
Following up on a number of discussions and requests we had in st. Goar, please find here a recap of pointers to FAO data used within NeOn.
You are welcome to use this data for non-profit purposes, granted that appropriate credits are given. Also, we appreciate that you inform us when utilizing this data, as your findings may also be of interest to us.
Your comments and feedback are warmly welcome, as a valuable input to improve the data.
Cheers
Caterina
